  "texts": [
    "Some studies employed more advanced NLP techniques such as topic modelling and distributed word and document representations, though only a few of them attempted to explain which semantic aspects of a campaign description influence its eventual outcome.",
    "These studies used keywords as features within highly explainable logistic regression models.",
    "However, interpretation of such models assumes that the meanings of keywords are independent of context, which is clearly an oversimplification, especially in the case of abstract keywords.",
    "The accuracy of the interpretation of the keywords based on general-language dictionaries like LIWC depends a lot on their coverage and adaptation to the application domain in question, such as crowdfunding.",
    "Another unexplored issue relates to understanding predictive semantic characteristics of campaigns using a broader range of learning methods."
  ],
